'''恶性疟原虫'''（{{lang-la|''Plasmodium falciparum''}}）是一种[[原生动物|原生动物]][[寄生虫|寄生虫]]，是引发[[人类|人类]][[疟疾|疟疾]]的[[疟原虫|疟原虫]]的一种，由雌性[[疟蚊|疟蚊]]传播。该型疟原虫引发的疟疾是所有瘧疾中死亡率最高的一种<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Perlmann |first1=P |last2=Troye-Blomberg |first2=M |title=Malaria blood-stage infection and its control by the immune system |journal=Folia biologica |volume=46 |issue=6 |pages=210–8 |year=2000 |pmid=11140853}}</ref>。根据最近的2014年[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]的统计，2013年全世界的疟疾病例共有1.98亿例，估计造成584,000人死亡<ref>{{cite web|title=Factsheet on the World Malaria Report 2014|url=http://www.who.int/malaria/media/world_malaria_report_2014/en/|publisher=World Health Orgnization|accessdate=2 February 2015|date=2014|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328134536/http://www.who.int/malaria/media/world_malaria_report_2014/en/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=who2014>{{cite book|last1=WHO|title=World Malaria Report 2014|date=2014|publisher=World Health Organization|location=Geneva, Switzerland|isbn=978-92-4156483-0|pages=32-42|url=http://www.who.int/entity/malaria/publications/world_malaria_report_2014/en/index.html}}</ref>。

惡性瘧原蟲起源於在[[大猩猩|大猩猩]]中發現的瘧疾寄生蟲，約一萬年前的''{{le|Laverania}}''。<ref name=loy>{{cite journal|last1=Loy|first1=Dorothy E.|last2=Liu|first2=Weimin|last3=Li|first3=Yingying|last4=Learn|first4=Gerald H.|last5=Plenderleith|first5=Lindsey J.|last6=Sundararaman|first6=Sesh A.|last7=Sharp|first7=Paul M.|last8=Hahn|first8=Beatrice H.|title=Out of Africa: origins and evolution of the human malaria parasites ''Plasmodium falciparum'' and ''Plasmodium vivax''|journal=International Journal for Parasitology|date=2017|volume=47|issue=2-3|pages=87–97|doi=10.1016/j.ijpara.2016.05.008|pmid=27381764|pmc=5205579}}</ref>

